project_descr: PARTNERSHIP FOR GOVERNANCE REFORM IN INDONESIA

outputs.output_descr:
a)Active citizens’ participation and civic engagement in democratic political governance at national and local levels.
b)Increased level of civic awareness among citizens and number of citizens participating in political processes; increased number of access points for citizens to engage in essential political and policy issues; electoral system, processes and mechanisms enhanced and national, regional and local parliaments empowered and capacitated.

project_title: partnership for governance reform in indonesia
